title: Do you think Defi will overturn Trafi?
body: Defi is a revolutionary innovation. After years of development, Defi's infrastructure has gradually matured and has been favored by traditional capital. In the next ten years, will Defi replace Trafi? Give me your answer below.
author: 0xe5cFE9F9ff617A274960Dc84F82c03e5098b2d53
